Annotation Interface PhoneNumber

@Documented @Retention(RUNTIME) @Target(TYPE_USE) @TypeTag(restrictTo=String.class, validatedBy=PhoneNumber.Validator.class) public @interface PhoneNumber
Annotates declarations of type String for which the value, if non-null, must be valid E.164 phone number.
